HEADWORD: Tibio-
<hw>Tib"i*o-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A combining form used in anatomy to
indicate <xex>connection with</xex>, or <xex>relation to</xex>, <xex>the
tibia</xex>; <as>as, <ex>tibio</ex>tarsus,
<ex>tibio</ex>fibular</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tibiotarsal</ent>⟦br⟧
